Class DtnBundle

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nasa.jpl.iondtn.DtnBundle
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class DtnBundle
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    This class represents one DtnBundle that has been received by ION-DTN and that has to be handed over to the client application

                 long creation_time,
                 int time_to_live,

                 android.os.ParcelFileDescriptor payload_fd)
        Constructor that allows the instantiation of a DtnBundle with a ParcelFileDescriptor.
        Parameters:
        eid - The EID
        creation_time - The time that the DtnBundle was created. Is ignored when DtnBundle is sent.
        time_to_live - The time-to-live value that the DtnBundle had when being received by ION-DTN.
        priority - The priority class of the DtnBundle (Bulk, Standard, Expedited)
        payload_fd - The ParcelFileDescriptor pointing to the payload of the DtnBundle.

        creation_time - The time that the DtnBundle was created. Is ignored when DtnBundle is sent.
        time_to_live - The time-to-live value that the DtnBundle had when being received by ION-DTN
        priority - The priority class of the DtnBundle (Bulk, Standard, Expedited)
        payload_byte_array - The raw payload as byte array.
